description: Kyle Molyneux posted videos of himself on a fishing boat on social media as he left the island.
title: Man who fled the Isle of Man on a fishing boat arrested
title_page: Man who fled the Isle of Man on a fishing boat arrested - BBC News
maintext: It is not known exactly when he left but he stopped responding to police on 8 July and subsequently posted a video of himself on a fishing boat to his Snapchat account.
